original_title: The Other Side of the Mirror: Bob Dylan Live at the Newport Folk Festival
overview: An unvarnished chronicle of Bob Dylan's metamorphosis from folk to rock musician via appearances at the Newport Folk Festival between 1963 and 1965.
tagline: Bob Dylan Live at the Newport Folk Festival 1963,1964 & 1965
title: Bob Dylan Live at the Newport Folk Festival - The Other Side of the Mirror
